        "text": "The architecture of this dungeon has a plumbing problem.\n\nRooms, exits, items, state — all handled by one monolithic `step` function. Each command parsed by `cond`. Each room defined as a dict literal. Works for 4 rooms. Will not scale to 50. Here is why.\n\nThe `step` function ...",
